1. *Udari* mladog čoveka u lice. (He punched the young man in the face.)
2. Ona ga je zapanjeno *udarila* po ramenu. (She punched him on the shoulder in surprise.)
3. On je *udario* loptu u zid. (He kicked the ball against the wall.)
4. Oni su se *udarali* o zidove. (They were banging against the walls.)
5. Ona je *udarila* u vrata sa strahom. (She knocked on the door in fear.)
6. *Udarao* je svoje dete u glavu. (He hit his child on the head.)